Package org.ietf.nea.pb.serialize.reader.bytebuffer

IETF TNCCS message byte buffer readers.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PbBatchHeaderReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS batch header compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageAccessRecommendationValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS access recommendation message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageAssessmentResultValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS assessment result message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageErrorParameterOffsetValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS error parameter with an error offset compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageErrorParameterVersionValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS unsupported version error parameter compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageErrorValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS error message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageExperimentalValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS experimental message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageHeaderReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS message header compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageImValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS integrity measurement component message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageLanguagePreferenceValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS language preference message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageReasonStringValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS reason string message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageRemediationParameterStringValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS string remediation parameter compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageRemediationParametersValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS remediation parameters message value compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbMessageRemediationParameterUriValueReader
    Reader to parse a TNCCS URI remediation parameter compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbReader
    Reader to parse an entire TNCCS message batch compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PbReaderFactory
    Factory utility to create a reader, that can parse an entire TNCCS batch compliant to RFC 5793 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
